{"title":"Esker Cycles Returns to Full Suspension with Aluminum & Titanium Frames w/ Orion","link":"https://bikerumor.com/esker-cycles-full-suspension-aluminum-titanium-frames-orion/","date":1741808003000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-hero.webp\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" alt=\"(Photos / Esker Cycles)\" /></p>\n<p>Roughly two years ago, Esker Cycles quietly paused their full suspension bikes. It was a move that went largely unnoticed, unless you happened to be in the market for one of their Orion suspension-equipped frames. But rather than getting out the full suspension game completely, it appears that Esker was just taking a break while completely redesigning the lineup (<a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/esker-cycles-hardtail-lineup-updated-hayduke-lvs-japhy-lorax-ti/\" target=\"_blank\">including their hardtails</a>). </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, Esker’s back in the full-suspension game, and they’re ditching carbon to focus entirely on aluminum and titanium frames. Esker’s new <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/howdy\" target=\"_blank\">Howdy</a> and <a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/pages/woodsy\" target=\"_blank\">Woodsy</a> models keep things refreshingly simple while still rocking Dave Weagle’s Orion Suspension System from their previous lineup.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-fist-pic.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-fist-pic.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension fist pic\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-fist-pic.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-fist-pic-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-fist-pic-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-fist-pic-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-fist-pic-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-fist-pic-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photos / Esker Cycles)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Think of these bikes as their beloved hardtails with just enough rear squish added for extra comfort and control. No gimmicks, no fluff — just straightforward metal bikes with balanced geometry and simple mechanics at a solid value.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>Perhaps most interesting is the frame material options. For both models, you can choose from a full aluminum version or a titanium front triangle paired to an aluminum rear triangle. Both bikes are also built around 29 x 2.6″ tire clearance with UDH 148mm Boost dropouts, and threaded bottom brackets. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Howdy &amp; Howdy Ti (125mm – Trail Full Suspension)</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-the-racoon.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"468\" height=\"428\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-the-racoon.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension howdy the racoon\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-the-racoon.webp 468w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-the-racoon-297x272.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-the-racoon-120x110.webp 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Named after the “Good Outdoor Manners Raccoon” from that 1950s Forest Service campaign, some of us may remember that flannel-wearing raccoon who taught us not to litter and to be respectful in the woods. That’s as important as ever, and seems like  good inspiration for a bike name. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-e1741801463931.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"988\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-e1741801463931.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension howdy complete\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-e1741801463931.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-e1741801463931-297x229.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-e1741801463931-120x93.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-e1741801463931-768x593.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Howdy aluminum complete </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-ti-e1741801498587.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"687\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-ti-e1741801498587.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension howdy complete ti\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-ti-e1741801498587.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-ti-e1741801498587-297x159.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-ti-e1741801498587-120x64.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-howdy-complete-ti-e1741801498587-768x412.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Howdy titanium complete </figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The shorter travel model, Howdy is meant to pair a 140mm travel fork with the 125mm travel rear suspension. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What makes it tick:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Suspension:</strong> 125mm rear travel via Dave Weagle’s Orion Dynamics design </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Frame options:</strong> 6061-T6 alloy (front and rear) or titanium front (3/2.5 seamless, butted, cold-shaped) with alloy rear </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Geometry:</strong> Trail-oriented 64.8° head tube, 77° seat tube, 435mm chainstays, modern-but-not-extreme reach/stack </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Colors:</strong> Raw, Unicorn, or Salmon </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Other Frame Features:</strong> External cable routing, 73mm threaded BB, 148mm boost spacing, 29×2.6″ tire clearance, and a Universal Derailleur Hanger</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Howdy-geometry.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1490\" height=\"771\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Howdy-geometry.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Howdy-geometry.png 1490w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Howdy-geometry-297x154.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Howdy-geometry-120x62.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Howdy-geometry-768x397.png 768w\" /></a></figure>\n<figcaption>Esker Howdy Geometry</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Howdy-in-action.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Howdy-in-action.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension Howdy in action\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Howdy-in-action.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Howdy-in-action-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Howdy-in-action-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Howdy-in-action-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Howdy-in-action-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Howdy-in-action-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Woodsy (145mm Trail – Rowdy Full Suspension)</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woody-the-owl.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"718\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woody-the-owl.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension woody the owl\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woody-the-owl.webp 1024w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woody-the-owl-297x208.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woody-the-owl-120x84.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woody-the-owl-768x539.webp 768w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Named after another cartoon public service announcement, Woodsy Owl is the Forest Service mascot who’s been telling kids to “Give a hoot! Don’t pollute” since 1970. He’s still out there fighting litter and teaching environmental protection to new generations.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-alum.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"976\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-alum.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension woodsy complete alum\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-alum.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-alum-297x226.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-alum-120x92.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-alum-768x586.webp 768w\" /></a><figcaption>Woodsy aluminum complete </figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-ti.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-ti.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension woodsy complete ti\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-ti.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-ti-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-ti-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-ti-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-ti-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-woodsy-complete-ti-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a><figcaption>Woodsy titanium complete </figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The bike itself is a 145mm rear travel all aluminum or titanium/aluminum all-mountain bike. Pair it with a 160mm travel fork for an extremely capable build. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What makes it tick:</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Suspension:</strong> 145mm rear travel via the same Orion system </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Frame options:</strong> Same alloy and titanium combos as the Howdy </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Geometry:</strong> Slightly slacker with 64.5° head tube, 77.5° seat tube, 440mm chainstays, similar reach/stack philosophy </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Colors:</strong> Raw, Verde, or Ranchera </li>\n\n\n\n<li><strong>Other Frame Features:</strong> Same practical specs as the Howdy</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Woodsy-Geometry.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1484\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Woodsy-Geometry.png\" alt=\"Esker Woodsy Geometry\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Woodsy-Geometry.png 1484w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Woodsy-Geometry-297x154.png 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Woodsy-Geometry-120x62.png 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Woodsy-Geometry-768x397.png 768w\" /></a></figure>\n<figcaption>Esker Woodsy Geometry</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Woodsy-doing-rocks.webp\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Woodsy-doing-rocks.webp\" alt=\"Esker Cycles New Full Suspension Woodsy doing rocks\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Woodsy-doing-rocks.webp 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Woodsy-doing-rocks-297x198.webp 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Woodsy-doing-rocks-120x80.webp 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Woodsy-doing-rocks-768x512.webp 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Woodsy-doing-rocks-800x533.webp 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Esker-Cycles-New-Full-Suspension-Woodsy-doing-rocks-720x480.webp 720w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2>Pricing</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Both the Howdy and the Woodsy follow the same pricing structure. The aluminum frames start at $2,000 for the frameset, or $4,000 for complete bikes. To bump up to the titanium/aluminum frame, the pricing jumps to $3,500 for the frameset and $5,500 for the complete builds. Check out the site below for all the all the build options. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://eskercycles.com/\" target=\"_blank\">EskerCycles.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/esker-cycles-full-suspension-aluminum-titanium-frames-orion/\">Esker Cycles Returns to Full Suspension with Aluminum &amp; Titanium Frames w/ Orion</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"71ab745e2c7bbb90d404387b445f7ce3a30a8826cdc3e51e73c363697fb95d07","category":"Cycling"}